1
00:00:04,160 --> 00:00:05,919
You've had stomach pain for so long.

2
00:00:05,919 --> 00:00:06,919
Why didn't you come in for a checkup earlier?

3
00:00:07,320 --> 00:00:08,359
This is very dangerous.

4
00:00:08,880 --> 00:00:10,039
Once the test results come out,

5
00:00:10,199 --> 00:00:11,080
you must be hospitalized.

6
00:00:11,359 --> 00:00:12,560
It's an old problem.

7
00:00:12,599 --> 00:00:13,560
I'll be fine.

8
00:00:20,719 --> 00:00:21,440
(Jiaojiao's project)

9
00:00:21,440 --> 00:00:22,920
(is at a critical stage.)

10
00:00:22,920 --> 00:00:24,239
(Even if it costs me my life,)

11
00:00:24,399 --> 00:00:25,600
(I have to help her win it.)

12
00:00:31,800 --> 00:00:33,359
Youhua, come work for us

13
00:00:33,359 --> 00:00:34,240
at Wayne Design.

14
00:00:34,240 --> 00:00:34,880
Two months from now,

15
00:00:34,880 --> 00:00:36,320
at the Paris Architecture Design Expo,

16
00:00:36,320 --> 00:00:37,520
I'll make you the lead designer.

17
00:00:37,520 --> 00:00:38,840
I'll let the whole world witness

18
00:00:38,840 --> 00:00:40,280
the debut of this mysterious design master.

19
00:00:40,679 --> 00:00:41,240
Shiyi.

20
00:00:41,960 --> 00:00:43,240
I won't switch jobs.

21
00:00:43,960 --> 00:00:45,560
Jiaojiao and I are getting married soon.

22
00:00:45,719 --> 00:00:46,799
Her career

23
00:00:46,799 --> 00:00:47,880
is my career.

24
00:00:48,439 --> 00:00:49,799
Then I can only wish you both well.

25
00:00:50,159 --> 00:00:51,359
If you regret it,

26
00:00:51,359 --> 00:00:52,520
remember to come find me.

27
00:00:52,920 --> 00:00:54,240
I'm not talking about the job switch.

28
00:00:54,640 --> 00:00:55,840
I'm talking about the marriage.

29
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:01,359
Jiaojiao.

30
00:01:01,799 --> 00:01:03,719
You're carrying Youping's child now.

31
00:01:03,960 --> 00:01:05,519
You need to take good care of yourself.

32
00:01:05,519 --> 00:01:06,799
As for work,

33
00:01:07,560 --> 00:01:09,120
leave it to Youhua.

34
00:01:09,200 --> 00:01:11,079
Let my brother handle all the design plans.

35
00:01:11,159 --> 00:01:12,159
You just focus on the baby.

36
00:01:12,319 --> 00:01:13,719
Okay. I'll listen to you.

37
00:01:13,719 --> 00:01:14,400
Jiaojiao.

38
00:01:14,640 --> 00:01:15,760
What is going on?

39
00:01:16,159 --> 00:01:17,400
We're getting married next week,

40
00:01:17,560 --> 00:01:19,159
and you're pregnant with my brother's child?

41
00:01:19,760 --> 00:01:20,560
Brother.

42
00:01:20,920 --> 00:01:21,879
Why are you here?

43
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:25,439
You aren't following my sister-in-law, are you?

44
00:01:25,519 --> 00:01:27,280
I'm here about my stomach illness.

45
00:01:27,400 --> 00:01:29,120
I didn't expect to catch you two doing this.

46
00:01:29,200 --> 00:01:29,840
Youhua.

47
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:31,400
Don't think so filthily.

48
00:01:31,519 --> 00:01:33,280
Youping and I are innocent.

49
00:01:33,640 --> 00:01:35,760
You're already pregnant with his child,

50
00:01:35,760 --> 00:01:37,719
and you still have the nerve to say you're innocent?

51
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:38,719
Youhua.

52
00:01:38,719 --> 00:01:40,560
Youping and I used artificial insemination.

53
00:01:40,680 --> 00:01:41,519
Back then,

54
00:01:41,519 --> 00:01:43,040
he was taking stomach medicine to you.

55
00:01:43,040 --> 00:01:44,040
That's why he had the accident.

56
00:01:44,599 --> 00:01:45,560
Now he can only sit in a wheelchair.

57
00:01:45,560 --> 00:01:46,359
Besides me,

58
00:01:46,359 --> 00:01:48,000
who else would carry on his family line?

59
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:49,400
Doing this

60
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:50,920
is also for your Song family.

61
00:01:51,760 --> 00:01:53,200
You're marrying me,

62
00:01:53,560 --> 00:01:55,599
but having my brother's child?

63
00:01:55,799 --> 00:01:57,519
Listen to what you're saying!

64
00:01:57,519 --> 00:01:58,359
Song Youhua.

65
00:01:58,400 --> 00:01:59,560
I'm giving your brother an heir,

66
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:00,560
and you still criticize me.

67
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:01,400
How can I

68
00:02:01,400 --> 00:02:03,040
trust myself to you in the future?

69
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:06,280
Your brother will have an heir.

70
00:02:06,439 --> 00:02:07,519
Aren't you happy?

71
00:02:07,519 --> 00:02:09,120
You're even holding him back.

72
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:10,960
What kind of brother are you?

73
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:13,159
Pretending. Pretending to be sick again.

74
00:02:13,199 --> 00:02:14,599
If it weren't for you,

75
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:15,120
Youping

76
00:02:15,439 --> 00:02:17,000
wouldn't have become disabled.

77
00:02:17,159 --> 00:02:17,639
Mom.

78
00:02:18,159 --> 00:02:18,680
Sister-in-law.

79
00:02:19,199 --> 00:02:20,400
Don't argue with Brother.

80
00:02:20,599 --> 00:02:21,639
This is all my fault.

81
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:23,199
I'm useless.

82
00:02:23,199 --> 00:02:24,159
I became disabled.

83
00:02:24,840 --> 00:02:25,960
I dragged the whole family down.

84
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:28,080
Look at Youping,

85
00:02:28,080 --> 00:02:29,159
then look at yourself.

86
00:02:29,319 --> 00:02:30,840
You're both my sons.

87
00:02:30,840 --> 00:02:32,719
How can there be such a big difference?

88
00:02:33,080 --> 00:02:34,400
I'm telling you,

89
00:02:34,719 --> 00:02:35,759
within three days,

90
00:02:35,840 --> 00:02:37,240
move out of the wedding house.

91
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:39,039
Jiaojiao needs to rest during pregnancy.

92
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:40,159
Youping and I

93
00:02:40,159 --> 00:02:41,120
will go take care of her.

94
00:02:41,199 --> 00:02:43,000
If you delay me from holding my eldest grandson,

95
00:02:43,120 --> 00:02:44,759
then you're no son of mine.

96
00:02:45,159 --> 00:02:46,240
Let's go.

97
00:02:57,199 --> 00:02:59,599
Zhang Shiyi, let's get married.

98
00:02:59,599 --> 00:03:01,199
Really? You've finally made up your mind?

99
00:03:01,199 --> 00:03:02,599
I'll book a flight home right now.

100
00:03:02,599 --> 00:03:03,520
You can't go back on it.

101
00:03:03,520 --> 00:03:04,719
Next week, at the Civil Affairs Bureau.

102
00:03:04,719 --> 00:03:05,120
Hubby.

103
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:06,199
Mwah.
